snippet.title: Gameplay Trailer of Trash Sailors
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1132030/Trash_Sailors/

Website: http://www.fluckymachine.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/X2GvEfp
Twitter: https://twitter.com/veronicgrk
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/fluckyMachine
Reddit: https://www.old.reddit.com/r/fluckyMachine
Newsletter: http://eepurl.com/gAochv

Trash Sailors is a hand-drawn sailing action with co-op up to 4 players. Control a group of castaways by local or online multiplayer, and create the trashiest sailing team in history! Make your slapdash raft, fight with mutants, and trash your friendship!

Trash Sailors is coming out on PC in 2021!

#TrashSailors #couchcoop #raft
